<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink336">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi namvayiṟ</l>
<l>piriyalar pōlap puṇarntōr maṉṟa</l>
<l>niṉṟatil poruṭpiṇi muṟṟiya</l>
<l>veṉṟūḻ nīṭiya curaṉiṟan tōrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Alas! May you live long, my friend! </l>
<l>The man who united as though he would never part from us, </l>
<l>has traversed the desert, over which the sun rised high, </l>
<l>in order to satisfy attachment to wealth that does not last.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
